        "title": "Java and .NET application communication",
        "body": "<p>I don't think this is quite possible or if it is recommended to do... but is there a way to connect or comunicate or deploy Java and .NET application for method beside Web Services. I mean I understand there are Messaging server that allows Java application communicate to each other but I dont know if this can cross development environment, any suggestion about it or thoughts about this?<\/p>\n\n<p>I'm limited to web and desktop environments.<\/p>\n",
