            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1289392995,
            "creation_date": 1289392995,
            "body": "<p>We ended up writing our own implementation of Java-.Net communication protocol based on <a href=\"http://hessian.caucho.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hessian<\/a> (later added JSON as well), but Thrift is a valid option.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 4144579,
            "question_id": 4141456
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/51455e58f34759be5b125d1dd40ba740?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
