            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1289567056,
            "creation_date": 1289367129,
            "body": "<p>The virtual machines (JVM vs CLR) are not going to talk to each other except through some OS level open standard.  Shared Files (yuck), Sockets and Web Services come to mind. There is nothing that would allow you to call a .net subroutine from java or vice-versa.<\/p>\n",
